title: Pioneer Photo Albums EV-246CHLK Happiness Photo Album 4 x 6 Inch
description: This photo album features a chalkboard designer printed cover and a deluxe rounded bookbound spine. The album holds 200 photos up to 4 x 6 inches in clear pockets with a shaded white paper background. There is a memo writing area next to each pocket. Photos are displayed two per page. Archival, photo safe: acid, lignin and PVC free. Item measures approximately 1.75 x 9.25 x 8.75 inches (L x W x H).
